title: Air Crash Investigations (Mayday) Season 1-11 [DVDRip]
description:
Air Crash Investigations (a.k.a. Mayday)
DVD rip of series 1 through 11

Series 1 is voiced by David Bamber, while all the others are voiced by the
usual Jonathan Aris (British accent).

English stereo only and no subtitles (none were on the DVDs).

The files are encoded in constant-quality mode so the file sizes vary quite a
bit, depending on the amount of motion in each episode.  But I figure the days
are long gone when each episode needed to fit on a CD-R, so it would be better
to aim for uniform quality across all the episodes instead.
